" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f9738117230cf444cb0c1e07a46ec13545e97c","tid":2362152,"uid":31314,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:03:11.000Z","msg":"唔睇都唔知，原來benz雄係名門之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n許紹雄的太公許應騤是慈禧太后的乾兒子，官拜一品，官至禮部尚書，閩浙總督，與李鴻章等清末名臣同朝，曾獲賜可在紫禁城騎馬。<br />\n<br />\n許紹雄的姑婆許廣平是魯迅第二任夫人<br />\n<br />\n許紹雄的叔公許崇智是參與創立黃埔軍校的粵軍總司令，早年參加同盟會，追隨孫中山參與辛亥革命、北伐等活動。1925年7月1日，中華民國國民政府在廣州成立，許崇智被任命為軍事部長兼廣東省政府主席。<br />\n<br />\n許紹雄的另一位叔公許崇清，許崇智堂弟，也留學日本並加入過同盟會。參加起草《中國國民黨第一次全國代表大會宣言》，歷任國民政府廣州市教育局局長、廣東省教育廳廳長、中山大學校長。<br />\n<br />\n許紹雄與名流許晉亨（李嘉欣老公）所屬的許愛周家族亦有親屬關係。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a247d90b7c19e2489a4da2a958f653dbde26ff2","tid":2362152,"uid":74332,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:07:39.000Z","msg":"Benz雄同林雪  企出黎唔講嘢都已經想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2ee0e73bd7c153658b5daa913274ee1e059c58","tid":2362152,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:22:46.000Z","msg":"叻"},{"pid":"a6d33d7b4c57e8755c3ac4753d6fdcc9107d7bc8","tid":2362152,"uid":188436,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:45:39.000Z","msg":"方鍾sir <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n方中信都係我地啲親戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06cd01330079482bd03f9689d1d0603bf426aab9","tid":2362152,"uid":50216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be5bc7312a7572bb4b3ea16b0cab2d8238a9c1c4","tid":2362152,"uid":71433,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"76991e8cba728910c241eef1862b6a616d575abe","tid":2362152,"uid":252588,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:56:58.000Z","msg":"第一張圖有聲<img src=\"/assets